### 创建一个测试课程（用于后续测试）
POST http://localhost:8080/course
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试课程",
  "brief": "这是一个测试课程",
  "mt": 1,
  "st": 2,
  "charge": "201001",
  "price": 0,
  "valid": true,
  "organizationId": 1234
}

> {% client.global.set("courseId", response.body.data); %}

### 添加课程教师
POST http://localhost:8080/course-teacher
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organizationId": 1234,
  "name": "测试教师",
  "position": "讲师",
  "description": "测试教师简介",
  "courseIds": ["211"]
}

> {% client.global.set("teacherId", response.body.data); %}

### 查询课程教师列表
GET http://localhost:8080/course-teacher/list/{{courseId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 查询教师详情
GET http://localhost:8080/course-teacher/1234/{{teacherId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 查询教师关联的课程
GET http://localhost:8080/course-teacher/courses/{{teacherId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 查询机构教师列表
GET http://localhost:8080/course-teacher/organization/1234
Content-Type: application/json

### 修改课程教师
POST http://localhost:8080/course-teacher
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{teacherId}}",
  "organizationId": 1234,
  "name": "测试教师",
  "position": "高级讲师",
  "description": "修改后的简介",
  "courseIds": ["{{courseId}}"]
}

### 解除教师与课程的关联
DELETE http://localhost:8080/course-teacher/{{courseId}}/{{teacherId}}
Content-Type: application/json 